sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Dev as Developer
    participant NPM as npm scripts
    participant Mod as SQLAlchemy models
    participant AL as Alembic
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant Seed as seed.py
    participant PT as pytest
    participant Team as Git and teammates

    Note over Dev,PG: PostgreSQL must be running
    Dev->>NPM: npm run db:up
    NPM->>PG: start container, wait until healthy

    Dev->>Mod: add or edit model in app/models/
    Dev->>Mod: register module in app/models/__init__.py

    Dev->>NPM: npm run db:revision -- "describe the change"
    NPM->>AL: alembic revision --autogenerate
    AL->>Mod: read Base.metadata
    AL->>PG: compare against current schema
    AL-->>Dev: new file in migrations/versions/, ruff-formatted

    Note over Dev,AL: Always read the generated migration
    Dev->>AL: review upgrade() and downgrade()

    Dev->>NPM: npm run db:migrate
    NPM->>AL: alembic upgrade head
    AL->>PG: apply schema change
    AL->>PG: record revision in alembic_version

    opt Demo data changed
        Dev->>Seed: update seed.py
        Dev->>NPM: npm run db:seed
        NPM->>PG: insert demo rows if table is empty
    end

    Dev->>PT: update tests (schema built from models)
    Dev->>NPM: npm run test:backend
    PT-->>Dev: pass or fail

    Dev->>Team: commit model and migration together, push, PR
    Note over Team: Teammates run npm run db:migrate after pulling
